      • getAppboyNavigator

        public static IAppboyNavigator getAppboyNavigator()
        Gets the current IAppboyNavigator class that defines the actions that should be taken when Braze attempts to display the news feed or open a URI from an in-app message. This will be null if none was set.
        Returns:
        The currently set IAppboyNavigator or null if none was set.
